<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.8">
<l>unti  yeḻunta vuruva malartaṉṉil</l>
<l>cantac catumukaṉ  taṉṉaip  paṭaittavaṉ</l>
<l>kontak  kuḻalaik  kuṟantu  puḷiyaṭṭi</l>
<l>tantamiṉcīp pālkuḻal  vārāyak kākkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">tāmota  raṉṟaṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having juiced a tamarind and poured [its juice] on the densely curled hair</l>
<l rend="indent">of he who created the beautifyl four-faced [Brahmā]</l>
<l rend="indent">on the shapely blossom that arose [from his] navel,</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb [his] curly hair with an ivory comb.</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the curly hair of Dāmodara!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
